at Court Philippe Chatrier.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9697054755911454, \"rank\": 0.025071134732291563, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And from the opening bell, chants of 'Imane, Imane, Imane!'\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"rang out around Roland-Garros' main tennis venue, which has been repurposed for thissummer's boxing finals at the Games.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024  Roared on by the rowdy crowd, Khelif went on to beat her Thai opponent in all three rounds by unanimous decision to secure a place in the final, where she will face off against Yang Liu of China.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\", \"score\": 0.960291520181818, \"rank\": 0.029412822867385776, \"text\": \"Thai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An in-form Khelif has now won 12 fights on the trot and the joy was clear to see as she celebrated her latest triumph, another defiant messagein the face of the 'bullying' she has received at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After shaking hands with Suwannapheng, the 25-year-old celebrated her progression to Friday's showpiece with a victory jig, which sent her already noisy Algerian supporters into a frenzy.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9697054755911454, \"rank\": 0.025071134732291563, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif will fight for GOLD!She won her 66kg bout against Janjaem Suwannapheng from Thailand to reach the Olympics final.Her reaction is priceless.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.69314345281196, \"rank\": 0.4167878525628076, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"May your glory be eternal sister!!\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"!pic.twitter.com/5iyiS85mtO  'I do not care what anyone is saying about me with the controversy,' Khelif said.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'All that is important to me is that I stay on the level and give my people the performance they deserve.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I know I am a talented person and this is a gift to all Algerians.'\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking ahead to her final bout against Yang Liu, Khelif vowed to 'give everything' to secure the gold medal for Algeria.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}, {\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9981767904875207, \"rank\": 0.001826522473926606, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am focused,' Khelif said.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am here for a good performance and my dream.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will give everything I have for the final.'\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suwannapheng said she was 'not afraid' of Khelif ahead of their semi-final and insisted the pair were 'evenly matched' despite the Algerian winning their previous meeting in India last year.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6349645756587878, \"rank\": 0.5730974782948001, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have improved since then and I will fight with all I have got,' Suwannapheng told Thai newspaperKhaosodearlier this week.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\", \"score\": 0.960291520181818, \"rank\": 0.029412822867385776, \"text\": \"Thai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Thailand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have looked into it too, about her hormones, and I know she's lost to female boxers before, but that was a long time ago.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am not sure if she's got stronger or if her male hormones have increased.'\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suwannapheng added: 'But if we meet again, I am not afraid because we are evenly matched.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have prepared my body well too, trained a lot.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think, no matter how strong or tough, we are both human, we both have two fists.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Having come this far, I want to go all the way to the gold medal.'\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Matthew Hudson-Sm